					"uidString" : "b1vI0vYnRL2OXh1um6uT4Q=="
				},
				"code" : "\"Fondo del Workbench a rojo — mira la ventana de FS-UAE al evaluar esto.\"\n| monitor viewport |\nmonitor := GT4AmigaMonitorClient default.\nviewport := monitor workbenchScreenPointer + 44.\nmonitor callLibrary: 3 lvo: -288 a0: viewport a1: 0 d0: 0 d1: 15 d2: 0 d3: 0"
			},
