				"code" : "\"Restaurar el azul estándar del Workbench 1.3: (r,g,b) = (0,5,10).\"\n| monitor viewport |\nmonitor := GT4AmigaMonitorClient default.\nviewport := monitor workbenchScreenPointer + 44.\nmonitor callLibrary: 3 lvo: -288 a0: viewport a1: 0 d0: 0 d1: 0 d2: 5 d3: 10"
			},
